198
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,000
Me?

199
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:23,760
Yes.

200
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:25,640
What’s wrong?

201
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:27,880
