202
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:29,240
No, no.

203
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:30,240
Relax.

204
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:32,280
I’ve told Mr. Fang about it.

205
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:33,520
